This fight was about Shell scripts, CHMOD and SSH.


Generate an SSH key pair: ssh-keygen -t [key_type]

Generate a public SSH key from a private key: ssh-keygen -f [private_key] -y > [private_key.pub]

Transmit a public SSH key to a remote server: ssh-copy-id [username]@[server_IP_address]

Connect to a remote server: ssh [username]@[server_IP_address]

Copy a file from a remote server using SCP: scp [username]@[server_IP_address]:[absolute_path_of_the_file_to_copy] [destination_location]


